oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Color tinted panoramic photograph of the 11th Cav. Regt. at Fort Oglethorpe, Ga.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This hand color tinted panoramic photograph shows the 11th Cav. Regt. formed for review on the parade ground at Fort Oglethorpe, Ga. Several buildings can be seen in the background. Fort Oglethorpe was located on the Chickamauga Civil War battlefield. The photo was probably taken in 1917 or 1918 during the World War, 1914-1918. Some of the buildings visible in the photograph are still standing in Fort Oglethorpe, Georgia, just south of Chattanooga, Tennessee.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: World War, 1914-1918; World War, 1914-1918 - History
